## ðŸ§° TOOLS REQUIRED (All Available on Kali)

| Tool                                    | Purpose                      |
| --------------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| `dd` / `dcfldd`                         | Disk imaging                 |
| `Autopsy`                               | GUI forensic analysis        |
| `Volatility`                            | Memory analysis              |
| `Wireshark`                             | Network capture and analysis |
| `Chkrootkit`                            | Rootkit scanning             |
